data.description: Located in the quite subdivision of Allamanda Grace within the Crescent Lakes Community. The master suite also located on the first floor with high ceilings leading upstairs and kitchen. The inside laundry area houses washer and dryer which convey with the sale. Outside the very private pool area benefits from no rear neighbors new fence and a screened in pool enclosure. Located on a corner lot, on a cul du sac.
